00:25:37,200 --> 00:25:37,720
<font face="Serif" size="18">姉</font>

332
00:25:37,720 --> 00:25:39,480
<font face="Serif" size="18">措置は庶民のために計る</font>

333
00:25:39,960 --> 00:25:41,320
<font face="Serif" size="18">革新こそが</font>

334
00:25:42,480 --> 00:25:44,760
<font face="Serif" size="18">君は享楽のために古い建物を壊した</font>

335
00:25:45,720 --> 00:25:46,840
<font face="Serif" size="18">無知です</font>

